"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-sport-paris-olympics-chief-faces-legal-probe-over-pay-source\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get the biggest sports news in your inbox  Tony Estanguet had so far been spared the legal problems that have embroiled other members of the Paris 2024 team.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.989343490289056e-22, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703099307, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 337, \"end\": 347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.542520156032163e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: AFP  PublishedFeb 06, 2024, 11:46 PM  UpdatedFeb 06, 2024, 11:46 PM  PARIS - French investigators have opened a legal probe into the pay of Paris Olympics chief organiser Tony Estanguet, a legal source said Feb 6, in an embarrassing development six months before the Games begin.\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 439, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975266853577246, \"rank\": 0.002124539360518868, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 533, \"end\": 547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The enquiry by magistrates specialised in financial crimes began \\\"last week\\\" and will look into the manner in which Estanguet receives his pay as head of the organising committee, the source said on condition of anonymity.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The triple gold medal-winning Olympic canoeist had so far been spared the legal problems that have embroiled other members of the Paris 2024 team.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 1013, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.542520156032163e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His annual remuneration of 270,000 euros (S$390,098) before tax and bonuses was made public in 2018 after a furore over reports that he would receive almost double that amount.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But according to revelations in the investigative newspaper Le Canard Enchaine last October, Estanguet uses his own company to bill the organising committee monthly, instead of drawing a salary.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesperson for the committee said it was \\\"astonished\\\" by the investigation and denied that Estanguet was paid as an external consultant in order to avoid salary caps placed on charities.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The package and arrangements had been approved by the board and the economy ministry, the spokesperson said.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The probe is a major blow for the suave 45-year-old Estanguet, the public face of the Paris Olympics, who is seeking to focus attention on preparations for the sporting events at the July 26-August 11 Games.\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics have been repeatedly tarnished by corruption in the past, either over the manner in which the Games were awarded or through the lucrative construction and services contracts that are part of the event.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The financial crimes prosecutors' office in Paris declined to comment when contacted by AFP.\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6189352708976564e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9869724701238389, \"rank\": 0.013199486571351487, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris organising committee was already the subject of three separate investigations into the possible misuse of public money and favouritism in the awarding of contracts.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2214, \"end\": 2219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6189352708976564e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The offices of the committee and Games infrastructure group Solideo have been searched by police, as have the homes of two other senior figures in the organising committee, Etienne Thobois and Edouard Donnelly.\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2559, \"end\": 2574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9tienne_Thobois\", \"score\": 0.9999993218032185, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Etienne Thobois\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9tienne_Thobois\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9tienne_Thobois\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those cases revolve in part around sports management or events companies founded by senior Games staff before they started working for the Paris 2024 organising committee.\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2737, \"end\": 2747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.542520156032163e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 20 different contracts are under the microscope, totalling tens of million of euros, one judicial source told AFP on condition of anonymity.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2888, \"end\": 2891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9869724701238389, \"rank\": 0.013199486571351487, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France's Anti-Corruption Agency had flagged possible problems with Estanguet's pay arrangement in a report in 2021 because of the organising committee's status as a charity.\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 3093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2920, \"end\": 2926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997231984748955, \"rank\": 0.0002747446045722104, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2929, \"end\": 2951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysian_Anti-Corruption_Commission\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anti-Corruption Agency\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysian_Anti-Corruption_Commission\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysian_Anti-Corruption_Commission\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The spokesperson said that his pay had been approved by the organisation's pay committee, composed of independent experts, and approved by the Economic and Financial Controller General in the economy ministry.\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3272, \"end\": 3279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_officer\", \"score\": 0.9999999998231033, \"rank\": 1.767050663806979e-10, \"text\": \"General\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_officer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_officer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given that Estanguet usually chairs the board, it had met without him when discussing his remuneration, the spokesperson said.\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers of Paris 2024 have been determined to showcase a different sort of Olympics, shorn of the common problems of vast over-spending, wasteful infrastructure investment, and corruption.\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3448, \"end\": 3458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.542520156032163e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a speech last month, President Emmanuel Macron called them \\\"a unique opportunity to show the best of ourselves, obviously in the sporting world... but also what our country represents and knows what to do in terms of exemplarity and organisation.\\\"\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3661, \"end\": 3676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both the French Anti-Corruption Agency and the state's top auditor body were given oversight of the organising committee in a bid to root out graft.\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 4027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3888, \"end\": 3894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975266853577246, \"rank\": 0.002124539360518868, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2016 Rio Olympics featured large-scale corruption, which shocked the general public, leading the former Brazilian Olympics boss and the governor of the city to be convicted afterwards.\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4033, \"end\": 4050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7560332809075118e-19, \"text\": \"2016 Rio Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several businessmen were also found guilty of bribing a Tokyo Olympics committee member in a scandal that soured the mood over the 2020 Games held in the Japanese capital.\", \"from\": 4219, \"to\": 4390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4275, \"end\": 4289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998640305, \"rank\": 1.360336612173999e-10, \"text\": \"Tokyo Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 4373, \"end\": 4381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9999849265445034, \"rank\": 8.567720969712338e-06, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the legal problems, the Paris Games appear broadly on track, with almost all of the main building work finished and the budget over-spend relatively small compared with past editions.\", \"from\": 4392, \"to\": 4583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This week will see the committee unveil the medal designs, while a brand new venue which is set to host the basketball and rhythmic gymnastics will open its doors at the weekend.\", \"from\": 4585, \"to\": 4763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Estanguet's basic pay of 270,000 euros is less than that of Sebastian Coe's when he served as chief organiser of the 2012 London Olympics.\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Coe, now head of the World Athletics, received around \\u00a3360,000 (S$608,990) in the year of the Games, according to the organising committee's annual report.\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 5060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4926, \"end\": 4941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999996948645, \"rank\": 3.049566904478637e-10, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024  France  Olympics  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 5062, \"to\": 5210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5077, \"end\": 5083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997231984748955, \"rank\": 0.0002747446045722104, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5127, \"end\": 5135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RSS Feed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 5211, \"to\": 5225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 5227, \"to\": 5244, \"entities\": []}]}"